 environment sensors J4 M IES record along track plasma densities velocities composition and drifts The data from the DMSP satellites are received and used at operational centers continuously The data are sent to the http www ngdc noaa gov National Geophysical Data Center s http www ngdc noaa gov stp stp html Solar Terrestrial Physics Division http www ngdc noaa gov NGDC http www ngdc noaa gov stp stp html STP by the http afw offutt af mil default htm Air Force Weather Agency http afw offutt af mil default htm AFWA for creation of an archive Currently data from 4 satellites 3 day night 1 dawn dusk are added to the archive each day For more information email mailto ngdc dmsp noaa gov ngdc dmsp noaa gov http www noaa gov NOAA http www ngdc noaa gov NGDC http www ngdc noaa gov stp stp html STP http spidr ngdc noaa gov SPIDR http afw offutt af mil default htm AFWA
